it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects

Interface Semantics

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Semantics.Cone<D>, Semantics.Cylinder<D>, Semantics.Orientable<D>, Semantics.Plane<D>, Semantics.Primitive<D>, Semantics.Sphere<D>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MORCone, MORCylinder, MOROrientable, MORPlane, MORPrimitive, MORSphere

    public interface Semantics
    General interface to define the mapping between an object and the semantics structure.

    An implementation example (based on aMOR library) of this interface is available in the package: it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects.aMOR

    REMARK: the unity of measure of the geometric quantities defined in this interface depends on how its implementation is instantiated.
    Good practice is to use the International System of Units (e.g.: meters)
